{"tha-ap104:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap104:0.2":"Bhikkhadayivagga ","tha-ap104:0.3":"2 Nanasannikattheraapadana ","tha-ap104:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap104:1.2":"Nisabhajaniyam yatha; ","tha-ap104:1.3":"Tidhapabhinnam matangam, ","tha-ap104:1.4":"Kunjaramva mahesinam. ","tha-ap104:2.1":"Obhasentam disa sabba, ","tha-ap104:2.2":"ulurajamva puritam; ","tha-ap104:2.3":"Rathiyam patipajjantam, ","tha-ap104:2.4":"lokajettham apassaham. ","tha-ap104:3.1":"Nane cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap104:3.2":"paggahetvana anjalim; ","tha-ap104:3.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap104:3.4":"siddhatthamabhivadayim. ","tha-ap104:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap104:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap104:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap104:4.4":"nanasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap104:5.1":"Tesattatimhito kappe, ","tha-ap104:5.2":"solasasum naruttama; ","tha-ap104:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap104:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap104:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap104:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap104:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap104:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nanasanniko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap104:8.1":"Nanasannikattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}